            "  MODEL_PATH - S3 path to model (e.g., s3://bucket/models)\n"
            "  MODEL_MANIFEST_PATH - Path to trusted model manifest with checksums\n"
            "  MODEL_KEY - Model identifier in manifest (default: 'default')\n"
